    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiny Boxes is a relaxing collection game, full of cute prizes. <br><br>Simply pick a box and get a prize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/2a1fea27fa4b0c6756286ff54d0aa624.poster.avif?t=1730244877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/2a1fea27fa4b0c6756286ff54d0aa624.webm?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/2a1fea27fa4b0c6756286ff54d0aa624.mp4?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade your prize in for coins, exchange it for another prize, or add it to your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/8120e7899790859166f169415b2470ea.poster.avif?t=1730244877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/8120e7899790859166f169415b2470ea.webm?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/8120e7899790859166f169415b2470ea.mp4?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete collections to unlock more boxes, earn coins, and gain stars to increase your level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/189ef2b56145c1bd30043526e5b63483.poster.avif?t=1730244877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/189ef2b56145c1bd30043526e5b63483.webm?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/189ef2b56145c1bd30043526e5b63483.mp4?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your coins to unlock even more boxes that hold even more prizes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/f515d637a74a63126711772bde8cf4d5.poster.avif?t=1730244877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/f515d637a74a63126711772bde8cf4d5.webm?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220860/extras/f515d637a74a63126711772bde8cf4d5.mp4?t=1730244877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What's in the box? Come find out!</p>",
